org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_DesignModel.HRM.HwLogical.HwComputing

Interface HwProcessor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ComputingResource, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, HwComputingResource, HwResource, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, ProcessingResource, Resource
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HwProcessorImpl

    public interface HwProcessor
extends HwComputingResource
    A representation of the model object 'Hw Processor'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Architecture
    • Mips
    • Ipc
    • Nb Cores
    • Nb Pipelines
    • Nb Stages
    • Nb AL Us
    • Nb FP Us
    • Owned IS As
    • Predictors
    • Caches
    • Owned MM Us
    See Also:
    HwComputingPackage.getHwProcessor()
